{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"910024cf4f","title":"山东农村鸣放出来的错误与反动言论","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"904b834fba","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":20,"articleId":"910024cf4f"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8b3a4c9856","type":"title","text":"山东农村鸣放出来的错误与反动言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"ae334e56a7","type":"paragraph","text":"现将山东省农村大放大鸣中，农民（主要是富裕中农）的一些错误言论和反动言论汇集报告如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"0b7ed7e231","type":"subtitle","text":"一、关于合作化方面：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"2a8ae4273c","type":"paragraph","text":"1、合作化不优越","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"83ca04b05e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）合作化优越，家家缺吃少喝，合作化好，缺粮又缺草，牲口死不少，人也吃不饱。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"614d490d73","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）办起合作社，庄稼差一倍，收入年年少，吃穿都不好，合作社好比老妈过年，一年不如一年。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"1872e41414","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）高级社没二年，又缺油，又缺盐，又缺粮草又缺钱，孩子哭，老婆叫，怎叫人不讨厌，高级社罪恶滔天。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"740adfca9d","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）入了社，活遭罪，干到老，穷一辈，要不早垮台，早晚死在内。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"0e68ae08d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）合作社内有三净（肚子净、粮仓囤子净、草园净）、三不够（粮不够、草不够、钱不够）。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"3731b4f105","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）减产、荒地和死牲口，也是合作社的优越性吗？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"ebdf85f40d","type":"paragraph","text":"2、合作社不如单干：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"b4bd5f7f93","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）单干好，单干好，又有粮，又有草，牲口长的壮，人也吃的好，今天吃过水面，明天吃水饺。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"0e447627e6","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）合作社好，地里长满草，单干不好，庄稼有人高。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"528da1be87","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）单干有三好（拾粪容易好，拾草多好，养兔子好），入社有三糟（庄稼长的糟、牲口养的糟、没吃没草烧）。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"18a986a63f","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）单干、单干，大米白面，合作，合作，样样都缺单干馍馍。互助饼，合作社的“糊都”照人影。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"7db878362e","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）政府是大地主，合作社是二地主，单干是自在主。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"121756e498","type":"paragraph","text":"3、合作化冒进了：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"fca723bfc6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）合作化好是好，就是步子迈大了。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"3de42bfb75","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）走社会主义的道，要一步步的来，单干到互助，互助到合作，不能一步登天。合作化走得太快了，都跟不上。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"7169b35846","type":"paragraph","text":"4、入社不自由：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"8ceaaf021d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）入了合作社，好比进了劳改队，样样不自由，活活遭洋罪。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"7c1b1c5287","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）参加合作社真是活遭罪，开支一、二元还得社里批，真不如单干自由方便。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"1136990f89","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）社员、社员，行动不便，开会太多，管理太严，不如单干，自在坦然。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"7c643f8d99","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）合作社好比公安局，走个亲戚赶个集，行动都不方便。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"47c8418681","type":"paragraph","text":"5、合作社是给贫农办的。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"a920b7ab63","type":"paragraph","text":"6、伙门楼先倒，合作社办不好，弟兄多了还得分家啦，何况这么多的户呢？","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"d9d7f0403d","type":"subtitle","text":"二、关于粮食方面","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"147859278a","type":"paragraph","text":"1、攻击和污蔑统购统销政策：","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"8a3103c33e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）统购统销是国富民穷的政策。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"54d7e1a9c1","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）统购统销是共产党的饥饿政策，搜刮民财，榨取老百姓的血汗。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"30411609c5","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）国民党不好，还没有统购统销政策，拿钱还能买出粮食，共产党好，还实行粮食统购统销，拿钱都买不出粮食。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"ad3b301614","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）统购统销好是好，撑死儿孙，饿死老子。够不够，三百六，饿死人，瘦死牛，挨饿受罪老农民，大米白面当官人。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"2dfda1c595","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）统购统销是干部大米白面，百姓汗滴禾田，忍饥挨饿遭洋罪；统购统销是条绳子，紧紧地系住老百姓的脖子。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"3cb38ba6ad","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）入了合作社，分的粮食少，主要是统购统销给搞糟了。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"893b12399d","type":"paragraph","text":"2、口粮和饲料留的太少，不够吃的：","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"a34fc78c92","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）三百六十斤口粮，就是躺下不干活，也不够吃的。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"d9d452b1d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）现在留的口粮还不如过去牛马吃的多。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"370c37cfe9","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）三尺肠子空着二尺半，吃不饱，干活没有劲，统购统销好在那里？","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"01ffc23881","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）现在是“地瓜社会”。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"b2baa10b14","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）农民口粮不够吃，农村粮食紧张，是国家买的太多，销的太少造成的。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"565de1644b","type":"paragraph","text":"3、国民党和洋鬼子时代还没有分配口粮的，吃多少是多少，共产党花得多，摆弄老百姓。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"0fdf63f1ae","type":"paragraph","text":"4、粮食紧张。不是粮商贩造成的，是国家把粮食运到苏联去了。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"d23c7b130b","type":"paragraph","text":"5、粮食统购的价格太便宜了，这是共产党剥削农民的毒辣手段。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"5bc9959a8d","type":"subtitle","text":"三、关于工农关系和产品差价方面","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"8e84b5b1ad","type":"paragraph","text":"1、工农生活差别太大：","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"4e37bb3389","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）工农生活一在天上，一在天下，差别太大了。各行各业都比农民生活好。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"5f512f1640","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）工人吃的好，穿的好，干的轻，还有劳保养老金，庄稼人苦海深，吃的糙、穿的破，干的还比工人重。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"36e1686f44","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）工人生活好比大地主，农民生活不如猪。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"6bc1316a5d","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）粮食、布票供应，为什么工人、市民要比农民多呢？这是共产党有意欺压老百姓。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"c6b338b87f","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）国家对农民不关心，城市盖电影院，戏院，闹阔气，叫老大哥享受，浪费的钱都是咱们农民的血汗。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"acf8fea3cb","type":"paragraph","text":"3、工农业产品差价太大：","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"641987d444","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）工农业产品差价太大了，工业品价格步步提高，粮食还是这个价，真是“谷贱伤农”。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"fea64d50d1","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）洋油、棉布、食盐太贵，粮食太贱。为什么五斤粮食买不到一斤洋油，三斤小麦买不到一尺布，一斤粮食买不到一斤盐。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"009ff476a6","type":"subtitle","text":"四、谩骂和污蔑基层干部：","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"8b2bed5a4e","type":"paragraph","text":"1、区干土皇上，乡干小阎王，社干是恶霸，队干翘尾巴（指狗）。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"ecec6e8c1f","type":"paragraph","text":"2、毛主席的经是好的，都叫下面的小霸王给念坏了。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"87b4315ccb","type":"paragraph","text":"3、坏蛋王八一大群（指基层干部），鬼鬼崇崇论纷纷（指开会），干的不知啥勾当，坑国家害人民。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"81687e681d","type":"paragraph","text":"4、共产党的干部是黄鼠狼子降老鼠，一窝不如一窝。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"af400dfe66","type":"paragraph","text":"5、农村的干部，是茶盘子摔在地上，没有一个是好的。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"21b87ee05b","type":"paragraph","text":"6、区委是吃冤枉粮的，工作组是吃剥削饭的，乡社干部是咱们农民养活的家狗。（摘自山东省委宣传部报告）","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"},{"id":"651a927e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：中共中央宣传部《宣教动态》（总第三OO期）一九五七年九月二十日。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f"}],"page":{"id":"708a2891f8","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"910024cf4f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}